Kathryn Erbe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathryn_Erbe 0 Kathryn Elsbeth Erbe (born July 5, 1965) is an American actress known for her role as Detective Alexandra Eames on Law Order: Criminal Intent, a spin-off of Law Order, and death row inmate Shirley Bellinger in the HBO series Oz.
